snippet.title: Castlevania Requiem: Symphony of The Night And Rondo of Blood  - Coming October 26, 2018
snippet.description:
Castlevania Requiem: Symphony of the Night and Rondo of Blood will be arriving exclusively to the PlayStation®Store on October 26, 2018. The collection brings the classic franchise to the PlayStation®4 computer entertainment system for the first time where fans can experience the saga of the whip-cracking, vampire hunting Belmont Clan.     

Pre-order today at: 
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP0101-CUSA13434_00-CASTLEVANIA00001
